text: awesome tasting ingredients with bee hoon. will definitely come back in future. opens early.
Delicious bee hoon, chicken wings n 鱼柳。 super friendly and hardworking couple. Say hi to them.
I like the hot and crispy chicken wing and ikan bilis. The chilli goes well with the nasi lemak. The price of $3.50 is very reasonable as the chicken wing is quite big and meaty.
Tasted nice, good attitude, cheap and fast service. It is rare to see other breakfast stall like this elsewhere.
in my opinion the best econ mee in singapore
